com.jswiff.swfrecords.actions
Class Push.StackValue

java.lang.Object
  com.jswiff.swfrecords.actions.Push.StackValue
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
Enclosing class:
Push
public static class Push.StackValue
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class contains a value which can be pushed to the stack. The default value is undefined, the type is TYPE_UNDEFINED. Use setters to change.

See Also:
